My potion to hair & scalp wellness 🪄 @mywishcare ‘s Hair Growth Concentrate has worked sooo well in filling in my hairline, reducing hair fall and maintaining well balanced scalp. 
Can’t recommended this enough to anyone and everyone!!
And if you’ve followed me a while, you know how much i love this, it’s a monthly empty and restock for me.
Here’s why
✨ What it does - A hair growth serums that revives your dormant roots.
✨ When/to Use - I say minimum an hour before hair wash. But I’ve even kept it on overnight. Can be used daily for best results or as often are you’d like.
✨ USP - Unlike alot of other hair growth products that l’ve tried for my hairline, this doesn’t sensitise or dry out the scalp at all. Also the spray nozzle is 100 times more hygienic compared to dropper formats used for majority of hair growth products. 
✨ What is has - Redensyl, Anagain, Bicapil, Caffeine, Basil, Rosemary & Rice Water 

I can’t get enough of this and can’t recommend this enough!
